data.description: Why rent when you can own this updated & well-maintained concrete block home? Split floor plan with high ceilings on city water in a great neighborhood close to shopping, schools, I-95 and a short drive to the beaches. Recently remodeled eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar. Formal living/dining rooms plus a family room with brick fireplace & built-in cabinetry. Large Master suite with ample natural lighting & a relaxing soaking tub. Two sets of sliders lead to two separate porches perfect for grilling & entertaining both leading to a cozy fire pit. Numerous updates including an extra wide driveway, new garage door, roof (2017), gutters, chimney, electrical panel, blinds, ceiling fans, light fixtures, shutters & more.  You will not be disappointed. Call today!
